{% callout type="danger" %}
## ⚡ SAFETY FIRST ⚡

**HIGH VOLTAGE EQUIPMENT**

The PSU-5000 series can output dangerous voltages and currents capable of causing SEVERE INJURY OR DEATH. Before operating this equipment:

1. ✓ Read the complete [High Voltage Safety Note](safety-note-psu-high-voltage)
2. ✓ Ensure you are qualified to work with high-voltage equipment
3. ✓ Use appropriate personal protective equipment (PPE)
4. ✓ Verify protective earth connection
5. ✓ Never work alone with high-voltage equipment

**If you are not qualified or trained to work with high-voltage equipment, do not operate this device.**
{% /callout %}
